37342>>>    Procedure OnBeforeShow
37345>>>        //  Hide header & apply nice background style
37345>>>        Send HideHeader to ghoWebApp
37346>>>        WebSet psCSSClass of ghoWebApp to "LoginBackground"
37347>>>    End_Procedure
37348>>>    
37348>>>End_Object
